of an impeachment. The law enforces a series

00:01:41.760 --> 00:01:44.960
of conditions for it to happen.

00:01:44.960 --> 00:01:51.700
The Brazilian Constitution requires a criminal
act from the President. But Dilma has not

00:01:51.700 --> 00:01:53.530
committed any crime.

00:01:53.530 --> 00:02:00.479
In fact, it is quite the opposite: she is
well-known as "rigid" and "inflexible", truly

00:02:00.479 --> 00:02:05.470
meaning that she is not open to illicit negotiations.

00:02:05.470 --> 00:02:11.920
